{"author":"Joe Oakhart","data":{"body":"Fix pushed to Gerrit as change 286 (https://rebar.solutions.navateam.com/c/rebar/+/286). Adds undocumented --include-provenance flag to `show`; default view now strips managed_refs, reconciler (_read_local_ticket_full) always passes the flag. Local: lint+mypy+34 affected tests green; verified end-to-end on kooky-graft-cap. Awaiting LLM-Review + Verified votes."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783226499197280001,"uuid":"0da006c4-1441-4c68-8a93-e2616309546d"}